General.Name: Southern Palladium Limited
General.Description: Southern Palladium Limited engages in the exploration and development of platinum group metals. It holds a 100% interest in the Bengwenyama Palladium/rhodium project located on the Eastern Limb of the Bushveld, South Africa. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
